  "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\nIn order to confgure the the lighthouse client, the lighthouse front-end will require system information about the host machine which the lighthouse client is running on.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\nAdd a new endpoint (/system?) for providing information for the host machine, such as drives, space available, CPU, memory usage, network stats etc\r\n\r\nAlso provide a socket event as system info changes.\r\n\r\n### REST Endpoints\r\n\r\n/system/drives: List drives available including full paths, names etc\r\n/system/stats: List all machine stats (CPU, memory, network etc)\r\n/system: all above\r\n\r\n### Socket Events\r\n\r\nsystem_stats: Current machine stats (as above) \r\n\r\n",
